833
00:59:31,318 --> 00:59:32,486
Aku berdebar lagi.

834
00:59:33,236 --> 00:59:37,074
Aku tak pernah berkhayal
akan mengusik saksi Babel.

835
00:59:37,657 --> 00:59:40,285
Kalau begitu, ayo cari tahu
tentang musuh mereka.

836
00:59:52,631 --> 00:59:53,590
Mulai.

837
00:59:54,216 --> 00:59:55,550
Cepat mulai.

